To run the code:

- Make sure that MonogBD, Nodejs and NPM are all installed.
- On the command line enter the directory and run `npm install` to install the dependencies.
- Navigate to 'data_gatherer/police'.
- Make sure the file 'importData.sh' is executable (`chmod +x importData.sh`).
- Run 'importData.sh' (`./importData.sh`) to load the crime data into the database. This may take some time so please be patient.
- Return to the root directory and run `node app.js` to start the server.
- Navigate to http://localhost:8080 to use the application.